title: Minister for Finance inspects building works at new €12.75m Clinical Education & Research Centre UHL ...
text: ( Source : University of Limerick ) Minister for Finance , Michael Noonan TD made a visit to inspect building works at the Clinical Education and Research Centre ( CERC ) which is under construction since June 2015 at University Hospital Limerick
